%% Key Agreement
sequenceDiagram
    participant pla as Privacy <br>Ledger A
    participant ra as Relayer A
    participant cc as Commit Chain

    autonumber

    ra->>cc: get pk's

    cc->>ra: <pk_1, ... , pk_n> 

    loop n times
        ra->>ra: Key Agreement
    end
    

    note over ra: obtain shared secret(s)
